[font=Impact][size=4][color=#eeece1]This time ICBINE comes in two flavors, CINEMATIC, and STRONG WARM, how to know which one is each from the screenshots and the trailer? Easy, Cinematic is the one with the black bars at the top and the bottom (don't worry, you can remove them in less than 30 seconds, just check the readme)
You don't like that obscure corners? thats the vignette effect, as easy to remove as the black bars, again, explanation in the readme.

....mmmmm trying to think stuff im forgetting but Im so tired and just want to sleep, lol.
99,9% of the issues are already fixed, just check the posts section of ICBINE 1 or 2...that's important because I'm not gonna answer fixed issues, please take your time and look for the fix in those posts sections.
If you liked it don't forget about that green button with the "endorse" word ;) good things happens when you click it! (maybe not)
